Всем привет!
Велосипед не мой, знакомые попросили помочь с поиском:

*Вакансия:* Middle Machine Learning Engineer
*Компании:* Powow AI
*город (если офлайн работа):* Odessa (remote work until the end of 2020)
*Что нужно делать:*
Design and implement ML models and solutions in Python (primarily in NLP domain);
Perform various types of NLP tasks related to business meetings in English (e.g., work on phrase type recognition, text classification).
Determine the required datasets and interact with the data team for their development;
Develop various models to solve the problems above (e.g., Random Forest, Bag-of-words, models based on vectorization);
Improve accuracy of existing deep learning methods and models;
Follow the latest research in machine learning, apply it to current challenges.
*Требования к кандидатам:*
2+ years of ML development;
Strong understanding of machine learning principles and model development workflow;
Experience in NLP subdomain (work with text);
Good understanding of NLP approaches, models, and libraries (Bert, GPT, spaCy);
Experience with at least one of the popular ML frameworks (TensorFlow, PyTorch);
Strong knowledge of Python;
Knowledge of Git, source code versioning, management
Excellent coding style and coding best practices.
*вилка зарплаты: $1200-$2200*
Write on <mailto:julia@guid.com.ua|julia@guid.com.ua>

